Duffle-bag
===

Duffle-bag (codename Myso) is an add-on creation and management application, currently only supports L4D2's VPK files. It is built in C with the GTK widget toolkit and libadwaita.

Duffle-bag is in active development and there is no stable build. In the future, there will be Flatpak and AppImage support.

Building:
1. Prepare dependencies as listed below this section;
2. Make shared libraries: `make libs`;
3. Make executables: `make execs`;
4. Executables are found in `bin/`.

Dependencies:
- bash
- getopts
- vpk (from pip)

